2052.subject: SBS
2052.descrlong: Complementary lab for SBSC 309. Addresses Major Learning Outcomes 1, 2, and 3. Participants engage in structured and collaborative online interactions that enhance their critical thinking skills and their ability to describe and analyze problems of theoretical relevance in the social and behavioral sciences. Formerly known as SBSC 311.
